{{#>container containerModifier="container--tall container--prose-width" innerClass="u-space-items"}}
  <div class="prose">
    <h1>Hey, I'm Paul!</h1>

    <p class="subhead">I design and code inclusive websites and web apps.</p>

    <p>
      I love switching back and forth between my sketchbook and code editor,
      obsessing over design systems, accessible interfaces, and performant code.
    </p>

    <p>
      I live in
      <a href="https://www.currentresults.com/Weather-Extremes/US/cloudiest-cities.php">sunny Portland Oregon</a>
      where I build accessible design systems and progressive web apps with the
      talented folks at <a href="https://cloudfour.com">Cloud Four</a>.
    </p>

    <p>
      In addition to designing and developing websites I enjoy
      <a href="/writing">writing</a>,
      <a href="/art">drawing</a>,
      gardening, cooking, and exploring the great outdoors.
    </p>
  </div>
{{/container}}


{{#>container containerModifier="container--tall container--prose-width" innerClass="u-space-items"}}
  <div class="prose">
    <h2>Selected Writing</h2>

    <p class="subhead">
      I enjoy writing to share knowledge and improve my own understanding.
      Here are a few of my favorite articles:
    </p>
  </div>

  <ul class="u-space-items">
    {{!-- TODO: Sort by priority? --}}
    {{#each (preparePosts collections.writing)}}
      {{#if data.isFavorite}}
        {{#> card
          link=(ternary data.isExternal data.externalUrl (url url))
          title=data.title
          headingTag="h3"
          description=data.description
        }}
          <span>{{prettyDate data.date}}</span>

          {{#if data.isExternal}}
              <span class="u-flex u-align-center">
                Written for
                {{#if (compare data.externalName "===" "Cloud Four")}}
                  {{>c4-icon iconClass="u-size2 u-space-left-7"}}
                {{else}}
                  {{data.externalName}}
                {{/if}}
              </span>
          {{/if}}
        {{/card}}
      {{/if}}
    {{/each}}
  </ul>

  <p><a href="/writing">View more articles →</a></p>
{{/container}}

{{#>container containerModifier="container--tall container--prose-width" innerClass="u-space-items"}}
  <div class="prose">
    <h2>Selected Work</h2>

    <p class="subhead">
      I enjoy creating side projects to experiment and push the boundaries of the web.
      Here are a few of my favorite works:
    </p>
  </div>

  <ul class="u-space-items">
    {{#each collections.work}}
      {{#if data.isFavorite}}
        {{#> card
          link=(ternary data.externalUrl data.externalUrl (url url))
          title=data.title
          description=data.description
        }}
        {{/card}}
      {{/if}}
    {{/each}}
    {{#each openSource}}
      {{#if this.isFavorite}}
        {{#> card
          link=this.url
          title=this.title
          description=this.description
          headingTag="h3"
        }}
        {{/card}}
      {{/if}}
    {{/each}}
  </ul>

  <p><a href="/work">View more work →</a></p>
{{/container}}


{{#>container containerModifier="container--tall container--prose-width" innerClass="u-space-items"}}
  <div class="prose">
    <h2>Getting in Touch</h2>

    <p>
      Outside of work you can find me gardening, hiking, cooking, or hanging out with my girlfriend and dog.
      Your best bet for getting in touch with me is reaching out over <a href="https://twitter.com/HaulPebert">Twitter</a>, <a href="https://github.com/Paul-Hebert">GitHub</a>, or <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/paul-hebert-20b75162/">LinkedIn</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
{{/container}}
